@startuml svc-media-gallery--post-media

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
    BoxBorderColor #94A3B8
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
    NoteBorderColor #64748B
    NoteBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

header [[/microservices/svc-media-gallery/#integration-context ⬆ svc-media-gallery Integration Context]]

title POST /media\nUpload a media item

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-media-gallery" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-media-gallery/]] #F1F5F9
participant "Object Store" as S3 [[/actors/#object-store]] #F3F4F6
participant "Google Maps Platform" as ExtMap [[/actors/#google-maps-platform]] #F3F4F6
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-media-gallery/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-media-gallery.html#/Media/uploadMedia View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /media
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> S3 : Upload binary file
activate S3 #F3F4F6
S3 --> Svc : OK
deactivate S3

Svc -> ExtMap : Reverse geocode GPS metadata
activate ExtMap #F3F4F6
ExtMap --> Svc : OK
deactivate ExtMap

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml